### REST API
# Criação de categoria

POST http://localhost:8080/category HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8080
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Category 3",
    "description": "Category 3 description"
}

###
# Busca de categorias

GET http://localhost:8080/category HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8080
Content-Type: application/json

###
# Busca de categoria por id

GET http://localhost:8080/category/57417f7c-ed7f-4024-a251-b96a06a836d2 HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8080
Content-Type: application/json

###
# Criação de produto

POST http://localhost:8080/product HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8080
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Product 3",
    "description": "Product 3 description",
    "price": 100,
    "image_url": "http://www.google.com",
    "category_id": "71a983f3-9b80-4eb1-aa55-0e4dbf6907f8"
}

###
# Busca de produtos

GET http://localhost:8080/product HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8080
Content-Type: application/json

###
# Busca de produto por id

GET http://localhost:8080/product/eb5f6d83-722b-45e3-8863-c4cf3907ef2e HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8080
Content-Type: application/json

###
# Busca de produtos por categoria

GET http://localhost:8080/product/category/5946c384-e84a-45b8-9e33-e06bace5882a HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8080
Content-Type: application/json

